{"tid":1892742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩姦羊犯被迫娶受辱羊","createTime":"2020-02-22T17:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T19:44:09.000Z","uid":198900,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed6776458d28ea0642b9f38c3bd7f7b068389a5","tid":1892742,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"非洲國家莫桑比克（Mozambique）兩名青年，早前跟一頭山羊大玩人獸交時，被警員捉個正着，除了面臨刑事起訴，山羊主人不但要他們賠償，還逼他們跟受辱山羊結婚。<br />\n莫桑比克是全球最貧窮國家之一，大部份居民都以務農維生，牲畜都是他們的重要資產，所以姆布庫塔村揭發人獸交案後，居民都議論紛紛，目擊者克里瓦說：「一名男子全身赤裸按着山羊頭，另一名男子則跟山羊性交。」<br />\n當局沒透露兩名強姦山羊的青年姓名和年齡，僅指兩人將會被控盜竊罪，但山羊主人卻不堪山羊受辱，威脅要對兩人展開民事訴訟，他更要求兩人賠償之餘，還要求兩人支付禮金，與受辱山羊依傳統儀式拜堂成親。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/art/20100228/13771196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20100228%2F13771196&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2Bdgrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=78407b00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20100228%2F13771196&h=78c5f995\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/art/20100228/13771196</a>"},{"pid":"b3f453a6e17abde9821885b6f78a4ddc76435d41","tid":1892742,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:35:41.000Z","msg":"如果我姦一條女 可唔可以同佢結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc36ece22fc426dc22960466c6803cde1feece9e","tid":1892742,"uid":49336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t5p9MmR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft5p9MmR.jpg&h=1a2d3c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgjt1Vc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpgjt1Vc.jpg&h=98d20821&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c633ebb5eedac324d0058310afc1b8ecece590fe","tid":1892742,"uid":21141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"reply